data.description: BEAUTIFUL RANCH WITH 4 BEDROOMS AND 3 FULL BATHS WITH FULL FINISHED BASEMENT! Updated to PERFECTION!! Eat In Kitchen with Gorgeous Updates including Fixtures & Hardware, Granite Countertops, Pantry Closet, Tile Floor, Fresh Paint, New Cabinets, and Slider to Patio!! Upgrade Stainless Steel Appliances with a Brand New Stove too plus New Storm Door on the Side Entrance! Main Floor Living Room is Large and Bright with Wood Flooring, Fresh Paint, New Blinds, and Scenic Bay Window! Main Floor Master with Private Bath - all Updated too! Plus Two More Spacious Bedrooms and another Remodeled Full Bath (New Flooring, New Vanity, New Toilet, Fresh Paint) to complete the Main Floor! Basement is Full Finished with Family Room Featuring Warm Fireplace, 4th Bedroom, Office, 3rd Full Bath, and Laundry Room with Storage and Washer & Dryer. Great Yard for the Kids, Mostly Fenced with Pergola area and Patio area! The 2.5 Car Detached Garage is fully loaded and finished with New Natural Gas Heater! Newer Sump Pump! This is a KEEPER! And won't last!!
